\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\insrsid4593572\charrsid4593572 Mother a great family storyteller.  High bourgeois background, no jobs, no education; father saw all this as a dangerous influence.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
