s great-grandfather, a Piquet, village school teacher, convinced by 1870 war that must learn German. Later generation, c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\insrsid15022078 .}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
