line had come to live with them in Toulouse in 1937.  Felix in 1930s anti-war, corresponding with Germans, depressed by onset of war, but Daniel his new hope.  Great storyteller: vocabulary.  Summers in Lescun, exploring forests together, Felix\rquote 
 animal stories \endash  taken up by Daniel.  Died 1947.   Back in S\'e8vres, walks in Pa}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\insrsid1651110 rc de St Cloud: story of \lquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
