\par Felix became close friend of Manotton, who was a mountain climber and hunter.  Initiated Pierre, who became fasc}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\insrsid9320055 inated by hunting; he also was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
