s walks around village with Felix.  Pierre\rquote s fear that Daniel would be the third generation, as in Thomas Mann\rquote s }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f40\fs22\insrsid4593572\charrsid4593572 Buddenbrooks.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
