elnau Basse.  Brothers Jean-Luc born in 1942, Michel in 1945.  De Gaulle 1945 picked Pierre, young intellectual, resistant, but not }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\insrsid9320055 c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
