\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\insrsid4593572\charrsid4593572 Isabelle then joined the research, and did most of the bakers\rquote  interviews.  Turning point at bakery shop in Bedous, near Les
cun, where presented themselves as working as a couple, and this won over the baker.  From this, contacts with many other local bakers.  Succeeded with the same strategy in Paris. Daniel likes interviewing, but shy of asking for an interview.  Wife of an 
anthropologist then interviewed the wives of the bakers.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\insrsid4593572 
