\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\insrsid4593572\charrsid4593572 Looked for statistics.  State figures on bread, but not on bakeries, or workers\rquote  hea
lth.  Most interesting statistic was the age structure, huge number of 15-19-year-olds, who soon leave the industry because of hard conditions.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\insrsid4593572 
