\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\insrsid4593572\charrsid4593572 Started the research without funding, on the bakery workers.  After three/four years, able to get fu
nding to pay Isabelle for two and a half years, for the bakers.  Wrote a two-volume report, finished 1981, but not published as a book \endash 
 due to friction over upbringing of older child.  Became impossible to continue working together.  Finds even writing with Catherine difficult, have to agree on every sentence.  Possible titles for book.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
