d asked for extracts in English which he would edit and weave together. No interview guide: a narrative interview, allowing interviewees to take control. Research group met a number of times: common spirit rather than common focus. Interviewees\rquote 
 childhoods dissimilar, but many felt themselves marginals, and surprised to find themselves leaders. All anti-Marxist. 
