Method demands two or more interviews in same family, of several generations, different genders. Can be done by yourself, by co-workers or by students. Rather than psychology, focus on social context, field of opportunities. Becau
se field is narrow, typically son of a worker is a worker; but son of village blacksmith is a mechanic. His belief that should not be too much psychology is influenced by Bourdieu, who says psychology is not sociology. But psychological information can be
 
used sociologically: the outcome of a psychological problem is shaped by economic and social resources, such as parents giving money to study. Joined a monthly meeting with well-known psychoanalysts trying to find a common language. Took one family, inter
viewed all members with a sociologist and psychologist \endash  let to very little. Psychoanalyst very dissatisfied by unresolved ending of interview with reluctant father.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\insrsid4593572 
